                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h3>Invest in an Exceptional Culture</h3>
                        <p>We strive to hire and retain talented people from diverse backgrounds</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="item">
                    <img src="https://i.imgur.com/Fw1l6Mt.jpg" alt="Core Value 3" style="width:100%; max-height:500px;">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h3>Embrace Integrity and Openness</h3>
                        <p>We value strong, positive relationships that are open and honest</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="item">
                    <img src="https://i.imgur.com/cbqI4rw.jpg" alt="Core Value 4" style="width:100%; max-height:500px;">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h3>Practice Responsible Stewardship</h3>
                        <p>We value stewardship and fiscal accountability and always strive to do more with less</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="item">
                    <img src="https://i.imgur.com/o6vTXSs.jpg" alt="Core Value 5" style="width:100%; max-height:500px;">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
